window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Grace had accepted that dabbling in the occult, traveling back in time, and banishing the spirit of a serial killer had more than likely led to her death. What she hadn't anticipated was what she would bring back with her when she returned to the world of the living.</p> <p>Armed with a battered soul, her fondness for sarcasm, and enough mental instability to keep a psychiatrist busy for a decade, Grace must navigate her new life with Beau and try to harness the supernatural abilities that death had gifted to her.</p> <p>Plagued by visions and the revelations of her family's magical past, Grace must fight if she is to have any hope of staying alive long enough to live out her happily-ever-after with her one true love.</p> <p>Some secrets should just stay buried.</p>"; 
